// osprey: flavor=ml
// ML-flavor must-reject. Pins [FLAVOR-ML-COMMENTS] (docs/specs/0024) and
// [DOC-SIGIL-ML] (docs/specs/0026).
//
// `(** … *)` is the ML documentation comment. Like the ordinary `(* … *)` block
// form it nests and must be closed; an unterminated one is a lexical error, not
// a silently-swallowed rest-of-file. The opener below is never closed.

(** Doubles its argument. The closing star-paren is missing on purpose.

double x = x * 2

print (double 21)
